      • getBatchCount

        long getBatchCount()
        The average batch size can be calculated by dividing getIdCount() by getBatchCount().
        Returns:
        the total number of times the ID generator has been used to generate a new ID batch since its LocalInstanceStats.getCreationTime().

      • getIdCount

        long getIdCount()
        Note that the ID count returned is the number of generated IDs not the number of consumed IDs.
        Returns:
        the total number of IDs generated (the sum of IDs for all batches) since its LocalInstanceStats.getCreationTime().
